a WebSocket slot on the orchestrator. Multi-slot workers reduce infrastructure cost by 3-5x at high concurrency while improving orchestrator scalability (fewer connections to manage). This creates a durable cost advantage that compounds with scale.\",\n    \"effort\": 8,\n    \"impact\": 9,\n    \"risk\": 7\n  }'","description":"Save idea 4: multi-slot cgroup workers"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":421,"cache_read_input_tokens":52728,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":421},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5ccd4a17-e6fd-4409-a07f-eea32410d852","uuid":"def678b1-5cae-4dd2-acab-42aef84b788c"}
